title: Microsoft Azure Virtual Machine: Memory
agents: azure
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check provides information about VMs available memory in the Microsoft Azure cloud.

 The thresholds can be configured using the rule "Available Memory".

discovery:
 One service is created on every VM host. The option "Map data to the VM itself" has to be configured in the Azure agent.
